<h1>Practice Blog Two</h1>
<p>Welcome to this Ruby on Rails Project</p>
<p>Created by Chibuikem Nwauche</p>
<p>Project Goals:</p>
<p>Seperate Users based on Roles and Giving them Defined Actions they can Perform</p>
<p>Showing the Associations between Models</p>
<p>Displaying how an Admin can see and delete all users assocaited with the porject except themselves</p>
<p>This Landing Page also Displays User Information Below</p>

<% if user_signed_in? %>
  <p> Hello Welcome to the website that can teach you about user roles</p>
  <p> Hello <%= current_user.username %></p>
  <p>Your Email is <%= current_user.email %></p>
  <p>Did you Know on our System you are a <%= current_user.role %></p>
  <p> You have successfully logged in</p>
  <br/>

  <% if current_user.role == 'Admin' %>
    <p>As the Admin of this Site you have various fucntions you can access</p>
    <p>You can view all Writer</p>
    <p>You can view all Posts Made by Writers</p>
    <% elsif current_user.role == 'Writer' %>
    <p>As a Writer of this Site you have various fucntions you can access</p>
    <p>You can create a Blog Posts</p>
    <p>You can view all Blog Posts made by all Writers</p>
    <p>You can view all Blog Posts made by Yourself</p>
    <% else %>
    <p>Seems you are an Unkown User</p>
  <% end%>

<%else%>
 <p>You are not Signed In therfore you cannot see any information  beyond this point </p>
  <%= link_to "Sign-Up", new_user_registration_path%>
  <br/>
  <%= link_to "Sign-In", new_user_session_path%>
<% end %>